										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Shadowheart doubles over in pain as her incurable wound flares intensely. Her parents also writhe in agony. Finally it abates and Shadowheart stands. Shar lowers the sword arm (right arm) out of view and gazes intently down at SH and co. Left arm still appears to be holding them up." />
										</node>
